gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

There the fruits are ripe and flowers have bloomed for nothing, nor has any path been crossed; 
The king's chariot is not to be passed, nor is the ocean of excess to be traversed;

Humanity is not found there, where humanity does not exist; 
If it exists, then nothing will come back; 
A person alone walks in the forest, no one fears greatly from anyone.

Here is the translation:

This path shows that tree, it has come to a small mountain range; 
That king's great name is Mahadattanama, all are Shyam Raj of Parvatiraj.
